\q1 and saw \add what was happening on\add* the earth.
\q1
\v 20 They will know that you hear prisoners groaning
\q2 and that you will set free those who have been told, “You will be executed.”
\q1
\v 21 As a result, people in Jerusalem will praise you [DOU] for what you\add have done\add*
\q2
\v 22 when many people \add from other people-groups\add* and \add those who are citizens ofother\add* kingdoms gather to worship you.
