\q2 \add I think that\add* I will ◄not remain alive very long/soon die►.
\q1
\v 24 I say to you, “My God, do not take me away \add from the earth\add* now,
\q2 before I become old!
\q1 You live forever!
\q1
\v 25 You created the world long ago,
\q2 and you made ◄the heavens/everything in the sky► with your own hands.
